{"tid":1930963,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"私家車撞開東華門直闖故宮","createTime":"2020-03-18T02:15:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T15:26:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"825363c80817c47748f5723b1d2f18491a40c879","tid":1930963,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T02:15:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200318/A6AHFBQTAVLG77725WDBYTQLVM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200318%2FA6AHFBQTAVLG77725WDBYTQLVM%2F&d=Ih%2BYJd3WmO0qFhbj2imzB%2BQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=73f51f9d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200318%2FA6AHFBQTAVLG77725WDBYTQLVM%2F&h=8e39215c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200318/A6AHFBQTAVLG77725WDBYTQLVM/</a><br />\n<br />\n私家車撞開東華門直闖故宮<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200318/large/1584462052_aada.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200318%2Flarge%2F1584462052_aada.jpg&h=28849353&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n私家車撞開東華門駛入故宮。<br />\n<br />\n北京故宮前晚深夜有私家車撞破東華門、長驅直入故宮範圍，肇事司機事後被警方帶走調查。故宮博物院官方微博昨證實事件並致歉，但未交代犯事者的身份和動機。<br />\n<br />\n微博刪片 肇事者身份成疑<br />\n<br />\n據內地媒體發放影片報道，涉事司機開車撞開東華門後，如入無人之境，再衝破三道物體防線，往太和殿廣場開去。環球網跟進報道指，事件發生在16日晚間，該私家車撞開東華門後駛入，有門釘被撞受損。拍片者表示，肇事司機曾對警方聲稱「有人要害他」。據悉，肇事司機已被警方帶走，事故原因還在進一步調查中。不過，相關影片在微博遭廣泛刪除，引起網民質疑肇事司機身份，質問：「為甚麼沒有任何警情通報，為甚麼秒刪視頻？」至昨日，故宮博物院官方微博回應表示，針對有網民發佈「周一開車進入故宮事件」，經查核屬實，對此深表痛心並向公眾誠懇致歉，並稱今後將嚴格管理，杜絕此類現象。惟故宮官方未有公佈調查結果。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200318/large/1584462052_d616.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200318%2Flarge%2F1584462052_d616.jpg&h=653d5cc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n東華門曾是供明朝太子出入紫禁城的通道。<br />\n<br />\n東華門為紫禁城東門，建於明永樂十八年（1420年），是專供太子出入紫禁城的門。清朝時，皇帝死後送殯迎靈都由東華門進出，所以東華門俗稱「鬼門」。早前故宮亦曾陷入輿論風暴，當時一名女子在微博發佈開平治車進故宮的照片，引發社會輿論關注。<br />\n<br />\n新浪微博"},{"pid":"bc2ec2e4c85d886de859a5cbface61cf7b5d9892","tid":1930963,"uid":186997,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T02:16:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/077b0a/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/d/attachments/day_200121/20200121_7f88fc12d9f7f8d5a184hpRKqllOPFxw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discuss.com.hk%2Ft%2F077b0a%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.discuss.com.hk%2Fd%2Fattachments%2Fday_200121%2F20200121_7f88fc12d9f7f8d5a184hpRKqllOPFxw.jpg&h=05df2dde&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"71a83a4b9ad149c9ebe1d14a255e44ca4633bce2","tid":1930963,"uid":74622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T02:16:48.000Z","msg":"支蟈不意外"},{"pid":"333ffc7affebc597f8c690be9d3067b3fae1e3ca","tid":1930963,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc2ec2e4c85d886de859a5cbface61cf7b5d9892","tid":1930963,"uid":186997,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T02:16:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/077b0a/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/d/attachments/day_200121/20200121_7f88fc12d9f7f8d5a184hpRKqllOPFxw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discuss.com.hk%2Ft%2F077b0a%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.discuss.com.hk%2Fd%2Fattachments%2Fday_200121%2F20200121_7f88fc12d9f7f8d5a184hpRKqllOPFxw.jpg&h=05df2dde&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T02:17:49.000Z","msg":"出現了"},{"pid":"085871158517b01d928fb830425b5b396d725f31","tid":1930963,"uid":131188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T02:30:17.000Z","msg":"勇士後門入帝宮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17828d3632c8aca74f84f34bba7e00592ed8d4da","tid":1930963,"uid":57214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T15:26:34.000Z","msg":"有习民要害朕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}